coverage_tag.MAN_BEATER: TPR vs Man > 1.25x vs Zone. Volatile, needs accurate QB.
coverage_tag.ZONE_MERCHANT: TPR vs Zone > 1.25x vs Man. High floor, game manager friendly.

script_tag.FRONT_RUNNER: Production drops >25% when trailing. Negative correlation with Opp QB.
script_tag.GARBAGE_TIME_HERO: Production jumps >25% when trailing. Positive correlation with Opp QB.

efficiency_tag.INEFFICIENT_VOLUME: High hog rate, low FP/target. High sensitivity to team play count.
efficiency_tag.HYPER_EFFICIENT: Low hog rate, high FP/target. Boom/bust independent of volume.

redzone_tag.RED_ZONE_DEPENDENT: >40% touches in RZ. Correlation = 1.0 with team RZ trips.
redzone_tag.BREAKAWAY_THREAT: >50% TDs from outside 10. Decoupled from RZ trips.
